metadata.description:
Doggo is used to things being a certain way in his family. He likes routine. Cat says hes become boring. That is, until Pupper shows up! Pupper is playful and messy, and turns the house upside down.

This card contains the following stories:
Doggo and Pupper
Doggo and Pupper Save the World
Doggo and Pupper Search for Cozy
A Macmillan Audio production from Feiwel & Friends.
metadata.author: Katherine Applegate
